<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Nice item, I was hunting outside of Karnor's one day and while my group was resting up I get ht'd for about 500 to 600 points of damage.  We weren't even looking for, she just came right up to the castle and nobody trained her to us either.  It was really strange, but anyways, my pet ate her pet for breakfast, but she was a royal pain.  I was lvl 43 at the time and the only thing I could get to stick on her was vampiric curse and my life taps, which neither were resisted.  It took alot of kiting to take her down but the thyxl is pretty nice and the look is well worth the effort.  As for her amount of hp, I'd say she has about 5k to 6k maybe even more.  Either way, expect a long fight.<BR>
